      "Text": "Security update for nghttp2",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for nghttp2 fixes the following issue:\n\n- CVE-2026-27135: assertion failure due to missing state validation can lead to DoS (bsc#1259845).\n",
